column1: The @AZDemParty just launched @MissionForAZ. It's a coordinated campaign that will win up & down the ticket this November. Follow them & get involved! #Election2020 #GetOutTheVote
We're collecting signatures to ensure I will appear on the ballot. In Arizona registered voters can sign nomination petitions on the Secretary of State's website: https://t.co/F3qCLELR6A
